---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken Breasts with Shallot Gravy, Fresh Salad and Buttery Mash
description: An ideal meal after a long day; this rosemary-seasoned, gravy-smothered chicken dish is perfection. A fresh salad and mashed potatoes top it off for a comfort-food extravaganza! Bon appetit!
